snippet.title: Guardian Tales | Season 3: Return Update
snippet.description:
World 19 X Revamped Content X Knight Ascension and so much more awaits!

‣ Event 1: 50 Free Summons! Summon your favorite hero up to 10 times a day for 5 days!
‣ Event 2: New World 19 'Pixie Forest' Opening Event!
‣ Event 3: 3,000 Gems just for logging in for a limited time!

• Check the official website for event periods and details on these and more!

Download FREE!: https://bit.ly/GTPlayNow
